text: IDRHNon-text-searchable PDFThis is an example of a non-text-searchable PDF. Because it was created froman image rather than a text document, it cannot be rendered as plain text by thePDF reader. Thus, attempting to select the text on the page as though it were atext document or website will not work, regardless of how neatly it is organized.
